The course provides framework for and builds links between the practical training sessions and enables to acquire methods in the specific field by supporting the student to prepare for and complete the practical training sessions and to reflect periodically among students and between the student and the supervisor.Objectives/eesmärkid:  The aim of the course is: - to enable the student to prepare for the successful completion of the practice and integration of the practice with previous learning experience;  - to facilitate the acquisition of specific methods of the chosen field.Learning outcomes/õpiväljund:  After completing the course, the student: - has an overview of most relevant institutions in the field of education; - is aware of the aims of practice and is able to plan his/her practice accordingly; - is familiar with practice regulations; - is familiar with the ways to complete practice and is able to use them.
